# Manage comments

You can display a list view of all comments. From the list you can choose to unpublish or delete one or more comments.

* Navigate to the comments management section of your site administration (a) In Drupal 6, click Administer and in the Content Management section click Comments. (b)  In Drupal 7 and later, click Content and select the Comments tab.
* Select one or more comments
* From the dropdown list select Unpublish or Delete.
* Click Update.

For information on setting permissions for comments, see the Managing Users section.
For information on specifying the comment settings for a content type, see the Structure Guide.
